text: H. Wade MacLauchlan (born December 10, 1954), is a Canadian academic and politician. He was 32nd Premier of Prince Edward Island from February 23, 2015 through May 9, 2019. MacLauchlan is openly gay. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian LGBT politicians Category:Gay men Category:LGBT academics Category:Premiers of Prince Edward Island
